```
drivetruck t2 l2_1 l2_3 c2
loadtruck p1 t2 l2_3
drivetruck t2 l2_3 l2_5 c2
unloadtruck p1 t2 l2_5
loadtruck p1 t2 l2_5
loadtruck p2 t2 l2_5
drivetruck t2 l2_5 l2_4 c2
unloadtruck p1 t2 l2_4
drivetruck t2 l2_4 l2_1 c2
unloadtruck p2 t2 l2_1
```
The plan moves p1 to l2_5 (satisfying the constraint's prerequisite), then transports both p1 and p2 efficiently in a single truck trip to achieve both goals with minimal actions.